<h1>BIFS Tutorials</h1><p>There are very few tutorials on XMT-A and MPEG-4 authoring available on the internet, and we are therefore very pleased to give you a step-by-step introduction to MPEG-4.
The following tutorial has been written for ENST's student in 2002, and has slowly been updated to the current stage. </p>
